(1, 2, 'Coding Dojo', 'coding-dojo', 1, '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Coding Dojo gives students a lot of bang for their buck, with a robust curriculum that includes more coding languages than its competitors. The beginner-friendly curriculum starts with programming basics before progressing into Python Full Stack and JavaScript Full Stack. For their last module, students can choose between Java Full Stack or C# Stack. By the end of the 14-week full-time program, students will be prepared to build a variety of projects, including user interfaces, ecommerce websites, login and registration pages, live-chat features, and more.</span><br></p>', 'Full-time Remote Software Engineering Bootcamp.', 1, 150, NULL, 50, 1724090400, 'uploads/bootcamp/thumbnail/coding-dojo-1727697609.jpg', '[{\"title\":\"Is a coding bootcamp worth it?\",\"description\":\"Coding bootcamps prepare individuals for a variety of careers in the tech field, including web developer, software application developer, software quality assurance engineer, database administrator, and business intelligence analyst. The Bureau of Labor Statistics predicts that overall employment in computer and information technology occupations will grow 15% by 2031.\"}]', '[\"Although most coding bootcamps are designed for novices without prior coding experience, they try to fit as much information as possible into their curricula, which can overwhelm students. We like that Hack Reactor offers a bootcamp that focuses primarily on Python and JavaScript, which are two of the primary languages coders need to know.\"]', '[\"Graduates from Coding Dojo often acquire proficiency in multiple programming languages and technologies, enabling them to build versatile and robust applications. The bootcamp\'s comprehensive curriculum covers a wide range of tools and frameworks.\"]', NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-01-01 00:02:20', '2025-01-01 00:02:20'),
(2, 2, 'CareerFoundry Web Development for Beginners Course', 'careerfoundry-web-development-for-beginners-course', 2, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span xss=\"removed\">It only takes five days to complete, and it’s entirely based on a project where you build your own website.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span xss=\"removed\">You’ll be introduced to all the major frontend concepts. This means creating the page using HTML for the markup, then CSS to style it, and JavaScript to make it come alive with functionality.</span></p>', 'This mini-bootcamp is a perfect way to create something tangible from the start.', 1, 150, NULL, 30, 1727805600, 'uploads/bootcamp/thumbnail/careerfoundry-web-development-for-beginners-course-1727778466.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-01-01 00:02:20', '2025-01-01 00:02:20'),
(3, 2, 'Data Science Bootcamp', 'data-science-bootcamp', 3, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Welcome to our Data Science Bootcamp, a dynamic and immersive 12-week program designed to introduce individuals to the exciting and ever-evolving field of data science. Whether you\'re a beginner or have some prior experience, this bootcamp caters to diverse skill levels, providing a solid foundation and hands-on experience in working with data.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Key Highlights:</span></p><ol style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Curriculum Overview:</span></p><ul><li>Delve into statistical analysis, machine learning algorithms, and data visualization techniques.</li><li>Learn how to extract insights from raw data and transform them into actionable strategies.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Real-World Projects:</span></p><ul><li>Apply your newfound knowledge to real-world scenarios through hands-on projects.</li><li>Develop a comprehensive portfolio that showcases your data science capabilities.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Flexible Learning:</span></p><ul><li>Our bootcamp is designed to accommodate both full-time and part-time participants.</li><li>Accessible online, allowing you to learn at your own pace from anywhere in the world.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Mentorship and Support:</span></p><ul><li>Benefit from guidance provided by experienced data scientists who will mentor you throughout the program.</li><li>Join a vibrant community of fellow learners, fostering collaboration and knowledge sharing.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Career Pathways:</span></p><ul><li>Explore potential career paths in data science, from data analyst roles to machine learning engineering.</li><li>Receive guidance on building a career in the data-driven industry.</li></ul></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Outcome:</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Upon completion of the Data Science Bootcamp, you can expect to:</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><li>Possess proficiency in statistical analysis and machine learning algorithms.</li><li>Demonstrate the ability to clean, explore, and visualize data effectively.</li><li>Showcase your skills through a portfolio of real-world data science projects.</li><li>Understand how to make data-driven decisions that impact business strategies positively.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Join us on this exciting journey into the world of data science. Enroll today and unlock a wealth of opportunities in the data-driven landscape!</p>', 'Embark on a transformative journey into the world of data with our Data Science Bootcamp. Tailored for aspiring data enthusiasts, this 12-week program equips you with the essential skills to navigate the data landscape. From statistical analysis to machine learning algorithms, our comprehensive curriculum, coupled with real-world projects, ensures you graduate with the expertise needed for impactful data-driven decision-making.', 1, 50, NULL, 20, 1727719200, 'uploads/bootcamp/thumbnail/data-science-bootcamp-1727778927.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-01-01 00:02:20', '2025-01-01 00:02:20'),
(4, 1, 'Cybersecurity Bootcamp', 'cybersecurity-bootcamp', 4, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Welcome to our Cybersecurity Bootcamp, a transformative 10-week program designed to empower individuals with the skills required to navigate and defend against the evolving landscape of cyber threats. Whether you\'re a novice or seasoned IT professional, this bootcamp caters to a diverse range of experience levels, offering hands-on training and real-world scenarios.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Key Highlights:</span></p><ol style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Comprehensive Curriculum:</span></p><ul><li>Explore network security, ethical hacking, cryptography, and incident response.</li><li>Gain a holistic understanding of cybersecurity principles and practices.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Hands-On Training:</span></p><ul><li>Engage in practical, real-world exercises using virtual labs and simulation environments.</li><li>Develop practical skills in identifying and mitigating security threats.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Mentorship and Guidance:</span></p><ul><li>Benefit from mentorship by seasoned cybersecurity professionals.</li><li>Receive personalized guidance and insights to navigate the complex cybersecurity landscape.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Flexibility:</span></p><ul><li>The bootcamp is structured to accommodate both full-time and part-time participants.</li><li>Access course materials and labs online, providing flexibility for remote learning.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Certification:</span></p><ul><li>Upon successful completion, receive a certification validating your skills in cybersecurity.</li><li>Enhance your credibility and employability in the cybersecurity field.</li></ul></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Outcome:</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Upon completion of the Cybersecurity Bootcamp, you can expect to:</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><li>Possess proficiency in identifying and mitigating security threats.</li><li>Demonstrate ethical hacking techniques and penetration testing skills.</li><li>Understand secure network configurations, encryption, and incident response.</li><li>Gain hands-on experience with industry-standard cybersecurity tools.</li><li>Receive a certification, validating your skills in the field of cybersecurity.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Equip yourself with the tools and knowledge to secure digital environments. Enroll in our Cybersecurity Bootcamp today and become a key defender against cyber threats!</p>', 'Immerse yourself in the world of cybersecurity with our intensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp. Tailored for individuals at all experience levels, this comprehensive 10-week program equips you with the skills and knowledge needed to defend against cyber threats. From ethical hacking to incident response, this bootcamp provides hands-on training, ensuring you graduate ready to safeguard digital landscapes.', 1, 100, NULL, 20, 1729706400, 'uploads/bootcamp/thumbnail/cybersecurity-bootcamp-1727779425.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-01-01 00:02:20', '2025-01-01 00:02:20'),
(5, 1, 'UX/UI Design Bootcamp', 'uxui-design-bootcamp', 5, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Welcome to our UX/UI Design Bootcamp, an 8-week program designed to ignite your passion for design and equip you with the skills needed to thrive in the dynamic field of user experience and user interface design. Whether you\'re a complete beginner or seeking to elevate your existing design capabilities, this bootcamp offers a comprehensive curriculum and practical projects to ensure a well-rounded understanding of the design process.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Key Highlights:</span></p><ol style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Comprehensive Curriculum:</span></p><ul><li>Dive into user-centric design principles, covering user research, wireframing, prototyping, and interaction design.</li><li>Explore industry-standard design tools such as Adobe XD, Figma, and Sketch.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Hands-On Projects:</span></p><ul><li>Apply theory to practice with real-world design projects that build your portfolio.</li><li>Receive feedback from experienced mentors to refine your design skills.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Flexibility:</span></p><ul><li>Structured to accommodate both full-time and part-time participants.</li><li>Access course materials and design tools online, providing flexibility for remote learning.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Mentorship and Collaboration:</span></p><ul><li>Engage with experienced mentors who provide guidance and insights throughout the program.</li><li>Collaborate with peers in a supportive learning community, fostering creativity and innovation.</li></ul></li><li><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Certification and Portfolio Development:</span></p><ul><li>Receive a certification upon successful completion of the bootcamp.</li><li>Develop a comprehensive portfolio showcasing your diverse design projects.</li></ul></li></ol><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Outcome:</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Upon completion of the UX/UI Design Bootcamp, you can expect to:</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\"><li>Demonstrate proficiency in user-centric design principles.</li><li>Create wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity designs for various platforms.</li><li>Understand user testing methodologies and incorporate feedback into designs.</li><li>Develop a professional portfolio that reflects your design capabilities.</li><li>Receive a certification, validating your skills in UX/UI design.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;\">Embark on a transformative design journey. Enroll in our UX/UI Design Bootcamp today and unlock the potential to craft exceptional user experiences.</p>', 'Embark on a creative journey into the world of UX/UI design with our immersive bootcamp. Tailored for both beginners and those looking to enhance their design skills, this 8-week program provides hands-on training in user research, wireframing, and prototyping. Build a professional portfolio and graduate ready to create exceptional user experiences.', 1, 200, NULL, 100, 1727719200, 'uploads/bootcamp/thumbnail/ux-ui-design-bootcamp-1727782654.webp', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '2025-01-01 00:02:20', '2025-01-01 00:02:20'),
