(249, 'Creating 3D environments in Blender', 'creating-3d-environments-in-blender-249', 'Learn Blender 3.2, 4.1, explore Geometry Nodes and create wonderful 3D environments', 1, 26, 'general', NULL, NULL, 'active', 'advanced', 'english', 1, 0, 66, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, 'uploads/course-thumbnail/-1722264596.jpg', 'uploads/course-banner/-1722264597.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTlsP6RfCQ8&t=271s', '<div data-purpose=\"safely-set-inner-html:description:description\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: \" udemy=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"sf=\"\" pro=\"\" text\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" \"system-ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";\"=\"\"><p style=\"max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">This fresh, new Blender 3.2 + 4.1&nbsp; course update (Version 3.0) contains valuable information for anyone looking to build 3D Environments. If you are new to Blender, it explains all the basics, teaching everything from grass to building creation, from scratch. If you’ve used Blender 2.81, this brand-new course highlights all the new Blender 3.2 features you can use to create amazing 3D environments.&nbsp;<strong>This course now includes an entirely new chapter focused on Blender 4.1</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><strong>Create beautiful 3D environments</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">Creating 3D environments is now more popular than ever, with a growing number of people mastering the skill of 3D crafting. Whether you are just starting out or already quite experienced, creating 3D environments can be a time-consuming and complex craft. During my 15 years creating these environments, I have faced and overcome many challenges. Having discovered the beauty and joy of 3D crafting, I now love nothing more than sharing my passion and wealth of experience with others. I hope this course sets you on the path to designing your own dream environment entirely in 3D.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><strong>Learn everything from A to Z</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">When I started 3D modeling, the only learning source I had was a printed book on random modeling. For me, it was enough to learn the basics, but without guidance, it’s easy to get lost. Today, there are many online learning resources that offer a swifter path to success in this field. However, not all offer a complete A to Z on 3D crafting. That’s why this 3D environment course is especially designed to cover everything you need to know to create stunning environments.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><strong>Step-by-step guidance</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">Discover everything you need to know to create your own 3D environments. Even if you have never touched Blender before, this course offers step-by-step guidance to help you with the basics so that you can feel comfortable using the software.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><strong>With 33+ hours of video content</strong>, this course takes you from complete beginner to proficiency.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">Best of all, it’s completely up to date. I developed the first version of this course in 2015 and I continually update and improve the content. In 2020, Version 2.0 covered the new Blender 2.8 UI, but the latest Blender 3.2 update meant it was time for another major overhaul. Version 3.0 has fully updated course material recorded in Blender 3.2, so you can follow along with ease.</p></div>', '{\"0\":\"Wanting to learn from scratch and step-by-step\",\"2\":\"PHP domain is recommended (the essentials are enough)\",\"3\":\"You will learn any additional requirement along the course (if you are missing something, just let me know)\"}', '{\"0\":\"Install Laravel on your System\",\"2\":\"Get all the confidence to build anything you want with Laravel\",\"3\":\"Create a high-level application while learning Laravel\",\"4\":\"Open your possibilities to multiple jobs and projects thanks to the Laravel popularity\",\"5\":\"Learn to configure Laravel according to your requirements\",\"6\":\"Master Laravel from the essentials to the advanced features\",\"7\":\"Learn Laravel and be part of one of the best web development communities\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Who is this course designed for?\",\"description\":\"This course is designed for intermediate to advanced developers who are familiar with the basics of Laravel and want to master its advanced features to create high-level applications.\"},{\"title\":\"What prerequisites do I need before taking this course?\",\"description\":\"You should have a solid understanding of PHP and Laravel basics. Familiarity with web development concepts and experience in building basic Laravel applications are recommended.\"},{\"title\":\"What will I learn in this course?\",\"description\":\"You will learn advanced Laravel techniques, including Eloquent ORM, advanced routing, middleware, event broadcasting, job queues, task scheduling, testing, and deploying high-level applications. You\'ll also delve into security, performance optimization, and integrating third-party services.\"},{\"title\":\"How is this course structured?\",\"description\":\"The course is divided into modules that cover advanced Laravel topics. Each module includes video lectures, practical exercises, quizzes, and real-world projects to reinforce learning and provide hands-on experience.\"},{\"title\":\"Will I receive a certificate upon completion?\",\"description\":\"Yes, you will receive a certificate of completion after successfully finishing the course, which you can share with potential employers or on professional networking sites.\"}]', '[\"1\"]', 0, '2025-01-01 09:06:47', '2025-01-01 09:06:47', 0, '{\"lesson_completion_role\":\"percentage\",\"minimum_duration\":15,\"minimum_percentage\":\"30\",\"locked_lesson_message\":\"&lt;h3 xss=&quot;removed&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span xss=&quot;removed&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Permission denied!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p xss=&quot;removed&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;span xss=&quot;removed&quot;&gt;This course supports drip content, so you must complete the previous lessons.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\"}', NULL),
