s and fundamentals of graphic design, all the way to creating beautiful products, learning about UX/UI and interactions, and creating a full design process for you to use with all of your future projects and clients.&nbsp;<strong>We pretty much cover it all so that the next time you are in charge of designing a product you have the step by step outline and guide to work as a professional designer.</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">We are going to teach you the skills that will allow you to charge a lot of money for your time. Not to compete for a few dollars an hour on some random freelancing websites.<strong>&nbsp;The goal is to give you the skills of a top designer, and along the way, we are going to design an actual product for a company that you will be able to add to your portfolio.</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">This course is not about making you just watch along without understanding the principles so that when you are done with the course you don’t know what to do other than watch another tutorial. No!&nbsp;<strong>This course will push you and challenge you to go from an absolute beginner to someone that is a top Designer that can get hired! Design is a valuable skill that doesn’t get outdated easily like most technical skills. Trends change, but the skills and fundamentals you learn in this course will take you many years into the future.</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><strong>This course is for you if:</strong><br><em>- You are a complete beginner looking to become a designer and freelance</em></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><em>- You are a designer who is looking to charge more for your work</em></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><em>- You are a developer who is looking to improve their design skills</em></p>', '{\"0\":\"Beginner Level knowledge of PHP\\/Laravel is required\",\"2\":\"Beginner Level knowledge of Vue is required\"}', '{\"0\":\"Learn how to Build Single Page Applications using Laravel 11, Inertia and Vue 3\",\"2\":\"Learn how to Build dependent dropdowns in Laravel and Vue\",\"3\":\"Learn how to build a Multiple Drag and Drop File Uploading and Processing with Laravel\\/Inertia\\/Vue\",\"4\":\"Learn how to implement Infinite Scrolling in Inertia Based Applications\",\"5\":\"Learn how to Implement Roles and Permissions on an Inertia based App (Without using any external package)\",\"6\":\"Learn how to Build Data-tables using Laravel, Inertia and Vue.\",\"7\":\"Learn how to Implement Translations in an Inertia based app.\",\"8\":\"Learn how to Customize Error Pages in Inertia\"}', '[{\"title\":\"Who is this course designed for?\",\"description\":\"This course is designed for developers who have a basic understanding of Laravel and want to learn how to integrate Inertia.js and Vue 3 to build dynamic, modern web applications.\"},{\"title\":\"What prerequisites do I need before taking this course?\",\"description\":\"You should have a basic understanding of Laravel, PHP, and JavaScript. Familiarity with Vue.js and the basics of front-end development (HTML, CSS) is also recommended.\"},{\"title\":\"What will I learn in this course?\",\"description\":\"ou will learn how to set up a Laravel 11 project with Inertia.js and Vue 3, manage state with Vuex, create and manage components, handle routing and authentication, and build a complete SPA (Single Page Application).\"},{\"title\":\"How is this course structured?\",\"description\":\"The course is divided into modules that cover setting up your development environment, understanding Inertia.js, integrating Vue 3, managing state, creating components, and building a full-fledged SPA. Each module includes video lectures, practical exercises, and projects.\"},{\"title\":\"Will I receive a certificate upon completion?\",\"description\":\"Yes, you will receive a certificate of completion after successfully finishing the course, which you can share with potential employers or on professional networking sites.\"},{\"title\":\"How can I get help if I have questions or need assistance?\",\"description\":\"You can ask questions and seek assistance through the course\\u2019s Q&A section or community forum, where instructors and fellow students can provide guidance and support.\"},{\"title\":\"Can I access the course materials after completing the course?\",\"description\":\"Yes, once you enroll, you will have lifetime access to all course materials, including any future updates.\"},{\"title\":\"What resources are included in the course?\",\"description\":\"The course includes video tutorials, downloadable resources, practical exercises, quizzes, and project files. Additionally, you will have access to a community forum for support and collaboration.\"},{\"title\":\"Are there any projects or hands-on exercises in the course?\",\"description\":\"Yes, the course includes numerous hands-on exercises and real-world projects that help you apply the concepts learned and build practical experience in using Laravel, Inertia.js, and Vue 3.\"},{\"title\":\"Do I need any special software or tools for this course?\",\"description\":\"You will need a computer with internet access, a code editor (such as Visual Studi