the basics of Laravel and want to master its advanced features to create high-level applications.\"},{\"title\":\"What prerequisites do I need before taking this course?\",\"description\":\"You should have a solid understanding of PHP and Laravel basics. Familiarity with web development concepts and experience in building basic Laravel applications are recommended.\"},{\"title\":\"What will I learn in this course?\",\"description\":\"You will learn advanced Laravel techniques, including Eloquent ORM, advanced routing, middleware, event broadcasting, job queues, task scheduling, testing, and deploying high-level applications. You\'ll also delve into security, performance optimization, and integrating third-party services.\"},{\"title\":\"How is this course structured?\",\"description\":\"The course is divided into modules that cover advanced Laravel topics. Each module includes video lectures, practical exercises, quizzes, and real-world projects to reinforce learning and provide hands-on experience.\"},{\"title\":\"Will I receive a certificate upon completion?\",\"description\":\"Yes, you will receive a certificate of completion after successfully finishing the course, which you can share with potential employers or on professional networking sites.\"}]', '[\"1\"]', 0, '2025-01-01 09:06:47', '2025-01-01 09:06:47', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(263, 'Home Improvement Business', 'home-improvement-business-263', 'Lighting planning, Plumber installations, Outdoor structure improvements, How to start home improvement business etc.', 1, 23, 'general', NULL, NULL, 'active', 'intermediate', 'hindi', 1, 0, 55, 35, 1, '', NULL, 'uploads/course-thumbnail/-1722260481.jpg', 'uploads/course-banner/-1722260481.jpg', NULL, '<div data-purpose=\"safely-set-inner-html:description:description\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 47, 49); font-family: \" udemy=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"sf=\"\" pro=\"\" text\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" \"system-ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" helvetica,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";\"=\"\"><p style=\"max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">The modern world culture and style has grown to the extent that elegance and beauty is the by word and every household want their home to be luxurious and conform to standard, home improvement can be upgrade of an existing home interior or exterior or other improvement of the property such as garden work or garage maintenance, the home improvement is done mostly on individuals personal preferences and comfort, maintenance or repair work making the home bigger by adding rooms/spaces as a means of saving energy or to improve safety.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.8rem; max-width: 118.4rem; font-family: &quot;Udemy Sans&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">In this current dispensation home improvement business is on the ascendancy and starting a home improvement business is a very good step in ensuri