(1454, 3, 'Lifelong learning is a journey, and you don\'t have to take it alone. Our LMS fosters a supportive community where learners of all ages and backgrounds can connect, share experiences, and motivate each other. Ask questions, discuss ideas, and gain new perspectives from a network of fellow lifelong learners. Together, we\'ll turn learning into a collaborative adventure.', 'Lifelong learning is a journey, and you don\'t have to take it alone. Our LMS fosters a supportive community where learners of all ages and backgrounds can connect, share experiences, and motivate each other. Ask questions, discuss ideas, and gain new perspectives from a network of fellow lifelong learners. Together, we\'ll turn learning into a collaborative adventure.', '2025-01-01 06:00:24', '2025-01-01 06:00:24'),
(1455, 3, 'Learn more about us', 'Learn more about us', '2025-01-01 06:00:24', '2025-01-01 06:00:24'),
